latestIgtvVideos.title: ALTOGETHER EVERYTHING BAGELS
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
We wanted to show you a snippet of our amazing bagel bake sale; we baked these fresh and shipped them a day before we closed down for the second lockdown! 
This time; when we reopen on 2nd June, we wanted to start with the same aroma of the insane seasoning, the honey poached bagels! 
While the kitchen team was busy packing and prepping for dispatch, @busyveee sneakily made the video and we are glad he did! ✨😂

LINK IN BIO TO PRE-ORDER!

latestIgtvVideos.title: O-Ren Ishii Coffee Tonic by @aj_coffeeninja
Orange Peel Ferment
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Trying our best to preserve the produce we use at A.T.E. Here in this picture is a jar of fermented orange peel in sugar salt white vinegar brine alongside some mint leaves 🌿
We carefully remove the pith of the orange peels so as to avoid any bitter taste in the ferment🍊 
Tasting notes include a sweet orange jammy mouthfeel with an aftertaste of Orange Liqueur! - @saa_bakes @theperfectmeasure .
.
#zerowaste #minimalwastekitchen #orange #orangepickle #orangeandmint #orangeferment #nowaste

latestPosts.caption:
Fresh, creamy & made to hit the spot, our Everything Bagel is the cool crunch your summer mornings need🥯

This isn’t your average bagel, think golden, fluffy everything bun, slathered with herbed cream cheese, topped with smooth guacamole and crisp cucumber slices for that perfect bite of flavor and freshness.

Light, satisfying, and full of texture. You can grab it solo or pair it with your go-to brew for the ultimate breakfast moment.

latestPosts.caption:
Bright, fruity, & ready for summer—our Mango & Raspberry Swiss Roll is here for a limited time only!

You’ll find our Swiss roll a little different than most; with a soft Japanese sponge cake rolled with a mango light buttercream, fresh mango chunks & raspberry confit.

You can order this as a small pastry or a whole Swiss Roll Log!
